Package: maudr
Title: Generate Data for Teaching Enzyme Kinetics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Lewis", "Ward", email = "u2283985@unimail.hud.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Jarek", "Bryk", email = "J.Bryk@hud.ac.uk", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Tool for generating, processing and visualising enzyme kinetics data for educational use. 
    Includes functions for assigning reaction conditions, simulating Michaelis-Menten and Lineweaver-Burk kinetics, 
    and generating individualised PDF reports for students.
